OL,6,FThe $3.8 billion set to vanish is from
OL,7,Fand would disappear over the next five
OL,8,Fto six years, the finance ministry
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FIt predicts the losses in 2024 would
OL,12,Fimpact Ghana's foreign exchange
OL,13,Freserves and exchange rate stability,
OL,14,Fleaving a "financing gap" in the
OL,15,Fcountry's budget.
OL,17,FThe bill has yet to be forwarded to
OL,18,Fthe country's president for assent.
