OL,6,FGhana's president said on Tuesday his
OL,7,Fgovernment will wait for a Supreme
OL,8,FCourt ruling before taking action on a
OL,9,Fbill.
OL,11,FPresident Nana Akufo-Addo said he
OL,12,Fsought to reassure the diplomatic
OL,13,Fcommunity that Ghana would not be
OL,14,Fturning its back on its longstanding
OL,15,Fhuman rights record.
OL,17,FAs a result, the ministry said the
OL,18,Fgovernment would need to significantly
OL,19,Freduce its expenditures or increase
OL,20,Fdomestic revenue.
